Package: MiniChip
Title: Analyze Chip Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michaela",
           family = "Schwaiger",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "michi@fmi.ch")
Description: This package helps with ChIPseq analysis. The function SimulatePeaks shuffles peaks (any GRanges object) in the genome. The function SummitHeatmaps calulcates and plots heatmaps around peak summits (any GRanges object).
